    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Replace this with a proper description.</em>\n<details>\n<summary>Credits and Instructions</summary>\n<h2>Made by Elwin</h2>\n<h3>Requires:</h3>\n<ul>\n   <li>Times-up</li>\n   <li>Elwin Helpers (Enable in Settings)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Optionals:</h3>\n<ul>\n   <li>Walled Templates</li>\n   <li>Sequencer (to support fog animation)</li>\n   <li>JB2A (free or patreon) (to support fog animation)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Usage:</strong></p>\n<p>This item needs to be used to activate. When first used, it opens the bottle and generates a smog cloud that follows its owner, \nand its size increases as long as the bottle is opened, until it reaches its maximum size. When used a second time it closes the bottle and the smog cloud position and size becomes fixed.</p></details>",
